OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Fheavy rain and strong winds will move
OL,7,Feastwards this evening. Rain clearing
OL,8,Fduring the early hours allowing some
OL,9,Fclearer spells and a few showers to
OL,10,Ffollow.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA brighter but breezy day
OL,13,Fon Wednesday with a mix of cloud and
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A few showers possible,
OL,15,Fespecially across the north of the
OL,16,Fregion. Temperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
